OL,3,CVictim: 'While others were building
OL,4,Ctheir futures, I was reliving my
OL,5,Ctrauma'
OL,7,FA rape victim has described having to
OL,8,F'relive her trauma in a courtroom
OL,9,Fwhilst others were building their
OL,10,Ffutures' as her attacker was sentenced
OL,11,Fto jail.
OL,13,FThomas Manson from Crediton was
OL,14,Funanimously found guilty at Bristol
OL,15,FCrown court before being sentenced to
OL,16,F57 months in prison for raping a
OL,17,Fteenage girl in Bristol in 2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
