OL,3,CVictim: 'While others were building
OL,4,Ctheir futures, I was reliving my
OL,5,Ctrauma'
OL,7,FThe 30-year-old, who has lifetime
OL,8,Fanonymity, reported the incident to
OL,9,Fpolice and Manson was arrested before
OL,10,Fbeing charged. After denying the
OL,11,Foffence, he was convicted by a jury in
OL,12,FOctober.
OL,14,FIn a statement read out in court, the
OL,15,Fvictim, who Manson met through a
OL,16,Fdating app, spoke about the long-term
OL,17,Fimpacts and the effect it had on her
OL,18,Feducation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
