OL,3,CVictim: 'While others were building
OL,4,Ctheir futures, I was reliving my
OL,5,Ctrauma'
OL,7,F"My A-levels suffered. I went from
OL,8,Fachieving A grades in my mocks to
OL,9,Freceiving Bs and Cs because of
OL,10,Fflashbacks and panic during exams.
OL,12,F"I have always dreamed of a career in
OL,13,Fcorporate law, but this path requires
OL,14,Ftop grades. Each time I apply for
OL,15,Fopportunities, I am forced to explain
OL,16,Fmy 'mitigating circumstances'.
OL,18,F"Every application reminds me of what
OL,19,Fhappened, and that it continues to
OL,20,Fhold me back."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
