OL,3,CVictim: 'While others were building
OL,4,Ctheir futures, I was reliving my
OL,5,Ctrauma'
OL,7,FShe said: "We fully recognise how
OL,8,Fincredibly difficult it can be to take
OL,9,Fthat first step and place your trust
OL,10,Fin the police, and I hope today's
OL,11,Foutcome gives her some sense of
OL,12,Fjustice and closure.
OL,14,F"I hope this sentence sends a clear
OL,15,Fmessage that we will do everything in
OL,16,Four power to bring those responsible
OL,17,Ffor such crimes before the courts, and
OL,18,Fthat victims who come forward will be
OL,19,Flistened to, believed, and supported
OL,20,Fevery step of the way."
